  <name>MonARCH Store</name>
  <summary>Universal Arch Linux App Manager</summary>
  <description>
    <p>MonARCH Store is a distro-aware software center for Arch Linux and compatible distributions (Manjaro, CachyOS). It discovers and installs packages from official repos, Chaotic-AUR, and the AUR with a single interface.</p>
    <p>Features include soft-disabled repositories, hardware-optimized CachyOS repos, one-click database unlock, and Polkit-based privileged operations. All sync and install operations use atomic transactions (pacman -Syu) to avoid partial upgrades.</p>
    <p>Created by cpg716 with the help of AI coding tools.</p>
  </description>
